# WhatsApp Cloud API (Meta Business) — connects your business number to this app.
# A "channel" in the WhatsApp phone app is not the same as API access; you need IDs from developers.facebook.com
#
# Steps: Meta for Developers → Your App → WhatsApp → API Setup
#   - Copy "Phone number ID" → WHATSAPP_PHONE_NUMBER_ID
#   - Generate a permanent access token (recommended: System User + assign app/asset) → WHATSAPP_TOKEN
#   - Optional: temporary token from API Setup works only for testing
# WHATSAPP_BUSINESS_NUMBER = your WhatsApp Business number in E.164 (e.g. India +91 7676348836 → +917676348836)
WHATSAPP_PHONE_NUMBER_ID=
WHATSAPP_TOKEN=
WHATSAPP_CHANNEL_NAME=Innovate Electronics
WHATSAPP_BUSINESS_NUMBER=+917676348836

